# Skills: repository placement

- Create new Agent Skills for this project only under **`<repo>/.cursor/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md`** (and nested files for that skill).
- Do **not** create or suggest personal skills in `~/.cursor/skills/` unless the user explicitly asks.
- On move or duplicate: source of truth is **`.cursor/skills/`** at the repository root.
